<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-45-0407 </DOCNO><TEXT>The covariant quantization of relativistic rings is performed in the BRSTformulation of path-integrals. BRST-invariant measures are constructedin the critical number of dimensions and the gauge independence of theresulting path-integrals is proved.</TEXT></DOC>